source.name: Approved Applications for Permit to Drill - Not Drilled:  As of Sept. 30, 2011
source.description: This table contains the total number of applications for permit to drill (APDs) by state that had not been drilled as of Sept. 30, 2011.  Oil and gas operators may not begin drilling activities on a lease without an approved APD.
